      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Hammad Bin Isa, from Hareyz, from Muhammad Bin Muslim, and Abu Baseer, and Bureyd and Fuzayl, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> and Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> both having said: ‘Allah<sup>azwj</sup> Imposed the <span class=\"iTxt\">Zakāt</span> along with the <span class=\"iTxt\">Salāt</span>’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from Hammad ibn ‘Isa from Hariz from Muhammad ibn Muslim and abu Basir, Burayd and Fudayl who have said the following: “Abu Ja‘far and abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhim al-Salam, have said that Allah has made zakat obligatory along with Salah (prayer).” "
        ]
      }
    }
